{"tid":474933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足球撚的自白","createTime":"2017-11-20T15:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T02:48:17.000Z","uid":130968,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a56e101b8a26da64d4273e2c35f018c929d9510d","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係一個學生，亦都係一個中意踢波嘅學生哥。因為細個果時生得高所以就比呀蛇拉去頂下波，做下柱，慢慢中意左呢項運動，踢得又唔算好差，負負碌碌比出面d教練拉左去踢d水平高嘅比賽。<br />\n一出到去見識，就知世界有幾撚大，同你一樣高但快過你嘅有，好撞過你嘅有，扭得過你嘅都有，個個都伊巴杜奧巴，但自己仲廢過利嘅卡路爾，好快就跟唔上，開始柒於人前，比教練屌就不在話下，帶埋老母去就基本嘅，隊友嫌棄你，有事冇事都屌撚柒你。咁我都明自己水平唔夠高唯有硬食，屌你都係想你進步。曾經有段時間比人屌到唔想去練波，但時間耐左都慣左，始終我中意踢波，我熱愛呢樣運動。<br />\n練波練得多就點都會有勞損，個人高大膝頭容易傷。出面勁個堆由細操到大，習慣哂個強度。而我就只係一個中學比人臨時拉夫頂替嘅柒頭。跟操左一段時間終於頂唔順，變左個傷膝青年，膝頭成日痛，好下停下頂到完季，睇埋物理治療休息左一排就做返gym想練好對腳。醫生睇過gym做過，一開操再傷。曾經有段時間踢完一課對腳痛到落唔到樓梯，我驚左條樓梯，squat都成問題。踢完一場就要抖抖到下一場，比賽要食止痛藥。傷下停下傷下停下，原本對足球嘅火就同對腳嘅軟組織一齊慢慢磨蝕。<br />\n每次一傷，教練就係到笑，問你點解對腳咁廢，我都想知點解。傷多幾次，連隊友都笑鳩你廢，話你藉口多多唔練波問你係咪詐傷。我冇回應d咩，但其實我好撚柒sad，有邊個想傷，有邊個唔想可以自由自在咁係草場跑跳頂，邊個唔想可以全力衝追撚住個波去跑然後大大力一野揪爆個龍。無計，我廢，所以我可以做嘅就只有忍，因為我廢，我冇話語權。有時傷有時痛都要忍都要練，因為我唔想比佢地睇唔起。<br />\n我冇同屋企人講過自己傷。香港地嘅父母一聽你玩運動就已經屌哂鬼，又話冇錢途哂時間。加上屋企窮，如果比佢地知我花時間踢波踢到傷哂要睇醫生實比人屌到甩肺，波都唔撚洗踢。我唔想比佢地有位入，因為我想踢波。<br />\n波齡話長唔長話短唔短，由一個放學跳級跳樓梯嘅後生仔到而家搭火車想坐嘅年輕人，我唔敢講自己付出左好多，但我絕對有犧牲過。或許我真係唔係呢個水平嘅人，夾硬做唔係自己水平嘅野，傷嘅只會係自己。有時見到關愛座，想座咪座囉，因為介意人地點睇而on99望住個位，真係幾笨。做人自私d，對自己好d，先會長命d。<br />\n<br />\n（有感而發，新手出post，咁長希望各位巴打高抬貴手屌細力d）"},{"pid":"c002c378687d09154ecb442168b7f8ce0fdd0d80","tid":474933,"uid":82698,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"Too long didn't read<br />\nSorry"},{"pid":"91507a0696305b350ec26da966f8d4bc20718fe8","tid":474933,"uid":7199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Too long didn't read<br />\nSorry</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a30a7d6ca06cd57af56b7e702513848ae185cb76","tid":474933,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:44:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"755aaf33048b4b0d3f6c62abe99a633a0e5c9af0","tid":474933,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今日個膝頭無啦啦痛，應該又踢唔到波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f9017034fd90abacb288da2e3e7c4b5f886473","tid":474933,"uid":9284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"半月板重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比啲on9仔當自己踢英超咁攔截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b7f347bed58703f7dd764e3c4c105f1338d316","tid":474933,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c2d38a3bdecca3487d4ff0fd8aba86a5a2d81","tid":474933,"uid":25172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"好鐘意踢波 無奈好易冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f50731207732b4d36067e7ae99219cea0faf4b4","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Too long didn't read<br />\nSorry</blockquote><br />\n比人拉去踢區隊<br />\n無幾耐做左傷追人<br />\n比教練隊友笑<br />\n<br />\n後面個part想坐開愛座我都唔明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我想達嘅係<br />\n如果傷左，咪抖囉，為左要面子為左啖氣，帶傷上陣，結果未好哂又整多獲，蝕底嘅只會係自己，始終健康最重要<br />\n就好似你明明整親腳想座關愛座，但又要介意人點睇，怕世俗眼光結果on99企係到，蝕底嘅咪只係自己<br />\n做人諗太多啦，自私少少對自己好d，人都開心d"},{"pid":"9bc474c94d3cfa51a986ecbfa3eb1c175f72e613","tid":474933,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"我都好鐘意踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但踢極都唔好"},{"pid":"4aa3a1ddc598d2e46815224ceb3e7f587604c646","tid":474933,"uid":64821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"今晚all in白禮頓啦"},{"pid":"5799aad835722e992b0455614eb8efd6a80c2532","tid":474933,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LET GO HAWKS</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f048dab84256ba3addf39548a9b5ed714011989","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好鐘意踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但踢極都唔好</blockquote><br />\n係香港玩運動真係唔係咁易 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d9b775b3edc03f9ebe327a2d2e0f6938b08e80","tid":474933,"uid":56680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"幾高幾重幾歲<br />\n老老實實 踢比賽唔岩你<br />\n得閒同frd踢下衛生波算啦"},{"pid":"8c9f3341f023067ce0c88d428279c693e96a6d53","tid":474933,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾高幾重幾歲<br />\n老老實實 踢比賽唔岩你<br />\n得閒同frd踢下衛生波算啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger 樓主其實唔洗咁chur"},{"pid":"4f7fd8633e449022dad3ebae04d93a64ba7a09b3","tid":474933,"uid":145138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"完全明白你，巴打加油！<br />\n踢下衛生波，唔好再去咁盡<br />\n希望唔好放棄自己既興趣"},{"pid":"d98ade84917b2744681f7ffbbc6b4d74ff2175a7","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾高幾重幾歲<br />\n老老實實 踢比賽唔岩你<br />\n得閒同frd踢下衛生波算啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger 樓主其實唔洗咁chur</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n188 82kg 歲就算啦 <br />\n放棄呢個念頭其實有，但係當你真心中意一樣野就自自然然想盡力做好，難得有機會想試多d睇自己去到幾遠，我個心好脆弱，成日會想放棄，但就衰個格硬頸 每次比隊友串比呀蛇屌個心就頂住頂住，我真係唔想輸比人睇，唔想衰比佢地，但對腳永遠都唔爭氣，其實做左傷追人咁耐，道火唔多唔少都蝕左好多，開始所有野都唔敢去盡，個心理多個關卡，結果打得差，又冇人support，然後重復loop過"},{"pid":"ed0b2d42da876fe5725c2e4e2433bc7fe9fedb77","tid":474933,"uid":1423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:33:47.000Z","msg":"唔係果種就唔係果種<br />\n你仲要玻璃，得閒踢下街波算啦<br />\n你估你外國球星有咁多軍醫backup你咩<br />\n去親醫院樣樣都係錢，算吧啦ching"},{"pid":"f6bb96b8658e2713c4dfe6435c218a7487748ddf","tid":474933,"uid":884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"身體質素嘅野天生就整定<br />\n無需太強求<br />\n好多人好強壯 踢極都唔傷 筋都唔會抽<br />\n有啲人又好易傷 踢一場要好耐回氣<br />\n依啲野冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a09d7d7bc63f4995a44867dcc29daacfc472fc","tid":474933,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"足球撚表示acl之後就掛靴<br />\n咁就一世"},{"pid":"a02c50becc0d1039ece009f41a1f5be5d88fca1f","tid":474933,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:38:34.000Z","msg":"樓主迪亞比？"},{"pid":"7e2bf8fc239ea8c02cfbed0c3de0995d1cb39e6f","tid":474933,"uid":122635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"入左佢地個世界，就知自己差幾遠。<br />\n<br />\n有時有d野真係無得強求，人生並非只得一條路。"},{"pid":"be186f0b275a3e61a082c9723cec2b4a1c6233ed","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身體質素嘅野天生就整定<br />\n無需太強求<br />\n好多人好強壯 踢極都唔傷 筋都唔會抽<br />\n有啲人又好易傷 踢一場要好耐回氣<br />\n依啲野冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都咁高咁大，點解你跑得快過火車，我轉個身都慢過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de72170b199d3b20b7049f1c53c238251cb4df1e","tid":474933,"uid":130968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主迪亞比？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f2ef80197660d90af1c682d332e69743c5d2fc","tid":474933,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T16:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主迪亞比？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改名做祖殊史密夫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}